a smart TV in your bedroom.

03:58.455 --> 04:01.589
So, W... Wow. So you're
watching us in the bedroom?

04:01.763 --> 04:04.461
Of course not.
I have a staff for that.

04:04.635 --> 04:06.550
- Why am I here?
- Oh, yeah.

04:10.293 --> 04:11.816
<i>Please!</i>

04:12.991 --> 04:13.818
